<exercise checkit-seed="0015" checkit-slug="M4" checkit-title="Finding a matrix inverse">
  <statement>
    <p>Show how to find the inverse of the matrix <m>C= \left[\begin{array}{cccc}
0 &amp; -1 &amp; -5 &amp; 8 \\
1 &amp; 1 &amp; 4 &amp; -1 \\
-2 &amp; -1 &amp; -2 &amp; -8 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; -3 &amp; 7
\end{array}\right] </m>.</p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <me>C^{-1}= \left[\begin{array}{cccc}
-13 &amp; -27 &amp; -14 &amp; -5 \\
-12 &amp; -22 &amp; -11 &amp; -2 \\
7 &amp; 14 &amp; 7 &amp; 2 \\
3 &amp; 6 &amp; 3 &amp; 1
\end{array}\right] </me>
  </answer>
</exercise>

